== 0.3.2 (06 Apr 2020) ==
   * no spatial weights calculation if spat.lag=FALSE 
   * now allows for integration of non-contiguous units (without lags)
   * extensive README file with examples added
   * various small updates and bug fixes

== 0.3.1 (31 Jul 2018) ==
   * new flexible logic for handling arguments based on "$" variable notation
   * corrected variable checks to remove a number of spurious warning messages
   * various small updates and bug fixes